 on the electrical properties of these foils like\nleakage current, stability, and discharges. At the detector level, we describe\nthe high voltage (HV) response, gain, uniformity, and stability. The GEMs have\nbeen proposed to have a wider applications, so we performed a feasibility study\nto utilize these for the imaging. We irrediated various objects of varying\ndensity with X-rays and reconstructed the images. The reconstructed image shows\na good distinction between materials of different densities, which can be very\nuseful in various applications like medical imaging or cargo imaging.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2022 08:00:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-10"}
