ows very closely the accelerator project\ndescription in the CLIC Summary Report for the European Particle Physics\nStrategy update 2018-19.\n  Detailed studies of the physics potential and detector for CLIC, and R&D on\ndetector technologies, have been carried out by the CLIC detector and physics\n(CLICdp) collaboration. CLIC provides excellent sensitivity to Beyond Standard\nModel physics, through direct searches and via a broad set of precision\nmeasurements of Standard Model processes, particularly in the Higgs and\ntop-quark sectors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2022 09:21:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2022 07:47:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-19"}
