te scenarios in which the FAS provides a\nperformance gain compared to the current multiple antennas solutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2022 13:42:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 28 Aug 2022 03:42:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Dec 2022 17:47:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
